msgstr "`op_statistic.csv`：算子利用率数据"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md:110
msgid "`step_trace_time.csv`: Scheduling data"
msgstr "`step_trace_time.csv`：调度数据"

