msgid ""
"`trace_view.json`: Chrome tracing format data, can be opened with "
"[MindStudio "
"Insight](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/mindstudio/81RC1/GUI_baseddevelopmenttool/msascendinsightug/Insight_userguide_0002.html)"
msgstr "`trace_view.json`：Chrome 追踪格式数据，可在 [MindStudio Insight](https://www.hiascend.com/document/detail/zh/mindstudio/81RC1/GUI_baseddevelopmenttool/msascendinsightug/Insight_userguide_0002.html) 中打开"

