msgid "host_system_usage_freq"
msgstr "host_system_usage_freq"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md
msgid ""
"Sampling frequency of host CPU and memory metrics. Disabled by default. "
"Range: integer 1–50, unit: Hz (times per second). Set to -1 to disable. "
"<br />Note: Enabling this may consume significant memory."
