"CPU和内存系统指标采集频率，默认关闭不采集。范围整数1~50，单位hz，表示每秒采集的次数。设置为-1时关闭采集该指标。<br "
"/>说明：开启该功能可能占用较大内存"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md
msgid "npu_memory_usage_freq"
msgstr "npu_memory_usage_freq"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md
msgid ""
"Sampling frequency of NPU memory utilization. Disabled by default. Range:"
" integer 1–50, unit: Hz (times per second). Set to -1 to disable. <br "
"/>Note: Enabling this may consume significant memory."
msgstr ""
"NPU Memory使用率指标的采集频率，默认关闭不采集。范围整数1~50，单位hz，表示每秒采集的次数。设置为-1时关闭采集该指标。<br "
"/>说明：开启该功能可能占用较大内存"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md
