#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md:316
msgid ""
"`return[0] | attr input_ids | len`: get the length of the `input_ids` "
"attribute of the first element in the return value."
msgstr "`return[0] | attr input_ids | len`：获取返回值中第一个元素的 `input_ids` 属性长度。"

